You can't put more than one

2739
01:55:52,018 --> 01:55:53,518
electron in a negative energy state.

2740
01:55:53,518 --> 01:55:55,518
So just fill it up

2741
01:55:55,518 --> 01:55:57,518
completely and call that empty space.

2742
01:55:57,518 --> 01:55:59,018
Having called that empty space,

2743
01:55:59,018 --> 01:56:00,518
what can you do to it?

2744
01:56:00,518 --> 01:56:02,518
You can remove one of the negative energy electrons

2745
01:56:02,518 --> 01:56:05,518
and put it back as a positive energy electron.

2746
01:56:05,518 --> 01:56:07,018
Sorry, put it back, yes, put

2747
01:56:07,018 --> 01:56:08,518
it back as a positive energy electron.

2748
01:56:08,518 --> 01:56:10,518
That leaves a hole.

2749
01:56:10,518 --> 01:56:13,518
And Dirac said that hole is

2750
01:56:13,518 --> 01:56:16,518
a particle of positive, uh, charge.

2751
01:56:16,518 --> 01:56:17,518
All right.

2752
01:56:17,518 --> 01:56:19,018
Now, at first he was very excited

2753
01:56:19,018 --> 01:56:20,518
because he thought it was the proton.

2754
01:56:20,518 --> 01:56:22,018
It's easy to prove that

2755
01:56:22,018 --> 01:56:23,518
the mass of the particle here

2756
01:56:23,518 --> 01:56:26,518
has to be the same as the mass of the...

2757
01:56:26,518 --> 01:56:28,518
These are particle and antiparticle.

2758
01:56:28,518 --> 01:56:31,518
This was the discovery of particles and antiparticles.

2759
01:56:31,518 --> 01:56:33,518
But this was the basic logic,

2760
01:56:33,518 --> 01:56:38,518
and it was equations like this which led to it.

2761
01:56:38,518 --> 01:56:40,518
Notice what a disaster you'd be in

2762
01:56:40,518 --> 01:56:44,518
if you tried to describe a boson by this equation.

2763
01:56:44,518 --> 01:56:47,518
That would be a madhouse.

2764
01:56:47,518 --> 01:56:49,018
You would just keep putting

2765
01:56:49,018 --> 01:56:50,518
particles into the negative energy state,

2766
01:56:50,518 --> 01:56:53,518
negative energy, lowest, as many as you like,

2767
01:56:53,518 --> 01:56:55,518
and there would be no ground state.

2768
01:56:55,518 --> 01:56:57,518
There would be no ground state.

2769
01:56:57,518 --> 01:56:59,518
You could just keep putting in more

2770
01:56:59,518 --> 01:57:01,518
and more and more negative energy bosons.

2771
01:57:01,518 --> 01:57:04,018
So this wave, this wave

2772
01:57:04,018 --> 01:57:06,518
equation only makes sense for fermions,

2773
01:57:06,518 --> 01:57:08,518
would not make sense for bosons.

2774
01:57:08,518 --> 01:57:11,518
And that was Dirac's great discovery,

2775
01:57:11,518 --> 01:57:16,518
that fermions can be described by Dirac equations like this

2776
01:57:16,518 --> 01:57:19,518
that would not make sense for bosons.

2777
01:57:19,518 --> 01:57:20,518
Why?

2778
01:57:20,518 --> 01:57:22,518
Just the reasons I explained.

2779
01:57:22,518 --> 01:57:25,518
And the idea of antiparticles.

2780
01:57:25,518 --> 01:57:29,518
We'll come to antiparticles for bosons next time,

2781
01:57:29,518 --> 01:57:33,518
and we'll discuss the Dirac equation in more completeness,

2782
01:57:33,518 --> 01:57:34,518
the real Dirac equation.

2783
01:57:34,518 --> 01:57:38,518
This is an elementary version of it.

2784
01:57:38,518 --> 01:57:43,518
But we'll come to it next time.

2785
01:57:43,518 --> 01:57:46,518
There's a number of things wrong with this electron.

2786
01:57:46,518 --> 01:57:48,518
For one thing, it only moves to the right.

2787
01:57:48,518 --> 01:57:49,518
That's the problem.

2788
01:57:49,518 --> 01:57:50,518
That's crazy.

2789
01:57:50,518 --> 01:57:54,518
For another thing, it moves at the speed of light.

2790
01:57:54,518 --> 01:57:56,518
That's crazy.

2791
01:57:56,518 --> 01:57:58,018
So there's a number of things

2792
01:57:58,018 --> 01:57:59,518
that are wrong with this electron.

2793
01:57:59,518 --> 01:58:02,518
It's a neutrino.

2794
01:58:02,518 --> 01:58:04,518
No, it's a neutrino.

2795
01:58:04,518 --> 01:58:08,518
No, it's a neutrino.

2796
01:58:08,518 --> 01:58:11,518
A neutrino is a boson.

2797
01:58:11,518 --> 01:58:14,518
A neutrino is a boson.

2798
01:58:14,518 --> 01:58:16,518
Yeah, this is a neutrino.

2799
01:58:16,518 --> 01:58:18,518
But it's not quite a neutrino,

2800
01:58:18,518 --> 01:58:21,518
because a neutrino also has mass.

2801
01:58:21,518 --> 01:58:25,518
For more, please visit us at stanford.edu.

